{"tid":1740250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美參院再通過香港保護法　禁向港警售催淚彈等鎮壓裝備","createTime":"2019-11-20T01:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T01:37:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2e511098ad79adb612a8c42e437f7cc127f86f74","tid":1740250,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:24:13.000Z","msg":"美國國會參議院取得議員一致同意，通過《香港人權與民主法案》。法案將交由參、眾兩院協商統一版本，提交總統特朗普簽署。<br />\n<br />\n另外，參議院亦通過《香港保護法》，禁止向香港警方出售催淚彈、橡膠子彈以及其他作鎮壓示威者之用的裝備。提出法案參議員魯比奧表示，美國向爭取自由的港人發出清楚訊息，美方將與港人同行。<br />\n<br />\n早前眾議院通過的法案版本要求美國國務卿，每年向國會提交報告，審視香港是否仍然有足夠自治，享受美國給予的特殊待遇，再決定考慮香港能否繼續根據《美國-香港政策法》，享有獨立關稅區特殊地位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493367-20191120.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493367-20191120.htm&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNoHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=33bf9a71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493367-20191120.htm&h=b3058913\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493367-20191120.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b5de045a50c0223a560a8430611f981368f27af0","tid":1740250,"uid":17381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a18cf97345f6cf027b55dee43cc52ee4b579364","tid":1740250,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d0a091f8bf1d41b01da38f8c45a8c32d7f4134","tid":1740250,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:35:02.000Z","msg":"屌 依家變左要聞支那毒氣<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>"},{"pid":"308895fedee1a5c78754fa4bf9635b16b91f9902","tid":17402